      "body": "%60%60%60cpp%0Aconst%20int%20tempPin%20%3D%20A0%3B%20%20%2F%2F%20Pin%20where%20the%20TMP36%20sensor%20is%20connected%0A%0Avoid%20setup()%20%7B%0A%20%20Serial.begin(9600)%3B%20%20%2F%2F%20Start%20the%20serial%20communication%20at%209600%20baud%20rate%0A%7D%0A%0Avoid%20loop()%20%7B%0A%20%20int%20tempValue%20%3D%20analogRead(tempPin)%3B%20%20%2F%2F%20Read%20the%20sensor%20value%0A%20%20float%20voltage%20%3D%20tempValue%20*%20(5.0%20%2F%201023.0)%3B%20%20%2F%2F%20Convert%20the%20value%20to%20voltage%0A%20%20float%20temperatureC%20%3D%20(voltage%20-%200.5)%20*%20100%3B%20%20%2F%2F%20Convert%20the%20voltage%20to%20temperature%20in%20Celsius%0A%0A%20%20Serial.print(%22Temperature%3A%20%22)%3B%0A%20%20Serial.print(temperatureC)%3B%0A%20%20Serial.println(%22%20C%22)%3B%0A%20%20delay(1000)%3B%20%20%2F%2F%20Wait%20for%201%20second%0A%7D%0A%0A%0A%60%60%60",
